      "question_fr": "[CB1#1] Dans $\\mathbb{C}$, $z = \\sqrt5 e^{-i\\pi/8}$ alors :",
      "choices": [
        {
          "label": "A",
          "fr": "$\\frac{\\sqrt{10+5\\sqrt2}}{2} - i\\frac{\\sqrt{10-5\\sqrt2}}{2}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "B",
          "fr": "$\\frac{\\sqrt{2+\\sqrt2}}{2} - i\\frac{\\sqrt{2-\\sqrt2}}{2}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "C",
          "fr": "$\\frac{\\sqrt{10+5\\sqrt2}}{2} + i\\frac{\\sqrt{10-5\\sqrt2}}{2}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "D",
          "fr": "$\\frac{\\sqrt{2+\\sqrt2}}{2} + i\\frac{\\sqrt{2-\\sqrt2}}{2}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "E",
          "fr": "Autre réponse"
        }
      ],
      "correctIndex": 0,
      "explanation_fr": "$z = \\sqrt5(\\cos\\frac\\pi8 - i\\sin\\frac\\pi8)$. $\\cos\\frac\\pi8 = \\frac{\\sqrt{2+\\sqrt2}}{2}$, $\\sin\\frac\\pi8 = \\frac{\\sqrt{2-\\sqrt2}}{2}$ → multiplication par $\\sqrt5$ donne A."
    },
